Conduct webPAS DR (Simulation  Test) - Hi Folks,

As discussed at our last meeting; outlined below, is the agreed scenario for
testing the forthcoming webPAS (SVHM) DR test.

Part a (5th July 2023)

1. advise the key users that Test 3 VM Server (SVHM-PASTEST-03 ------ VICDC2
SVHM), will be unavailable for the duration of the test. Action: (RM) to advise
users on 5th July (10 AM) that T3 wont be available until COB 6th July 2023.
2. take a backup of the T3 environment on the 5th of July, prior to shut down on
the 6th of July at 10:30 AM (or earlier if possible) Action: (SW) on 5th July
2023
Part B (6th July 2023)

* restore application VM (Test3) from DC2 to DC1 from the last successful backup
back taken. Action: (SW)
* after the application VM at DC1 has been restored and verified, advise team
members > (RM/MH/CB & RN) Action (SW)
* check that the relevant (test) database is connected to the T3 VM @ (DC1) that
has been restored. Action: (CB)
* Note: given that there is no impact to production or business services, we
wont need to raise a change record; but if needed, Brendan
can invite us to attend CAB and update the forum on this activity. RN to attend
CAB on 5th July to provide an update Action: (RN)

* Please advise by COB tomorrow if you have any concerns Info Only

Ps: Runsheet will be attached very shortly.

Look forward to seeing you all on the 6th of July .

Kind regards,
Richard
